return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2021-03-17 12:32:43+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Themes - Blossom Spa','language'=>'zh_CN','messages'=>['Blossom Spa'=>'Blossom Spa','Blossom Spa is a clean and beautiful WordPress Theme focused on Spa and Salon business. You can use this theme to create a fully functional and professional website for your business without prior knowledge or experience of coding. This theme is best suited for businesses like spa, beauty salon, wellness center, massage parlor, yoga studio, meditation classes, and natural health care or beauty businesses. It is a fully responsive and mobile friendly theme which automatically adjusts itself according to the screen sizes and provides the user with the best user experience. This theme comes with a clean and minimal design and provides user-friendly navigation. Also, this theme is developed with speed optimized codes that enhance your website’s speed. Furthermore, the theme also has Schema.org markup inbuilt to help Google understand your website better and rank higher. This theme also features a built-in live customizer which helps you to customize your website with live preview. The social media integration feature helps you increase your social media followings and also connect with your visitors in an effective way. This theme features different sections which are Banner Section, Service Section, About Section, Service Two Section, CTA Section, Team Section, Testimonial Section, and Blog Section on the homepage which is helpful in providing detailed information about your business in a proper way. This theme comes with an extensive documentation to help you build your website from scratch without any prior technical or coding knowledge. If you get any issue or have any questions related to the theme, you can contact the friendly support team. Check theme details at https://blossomthemes.com/downloads/blossom-spa-free-wordpress-theme/, demo at https://blossomthemes.com/theme-demo/?theme=blossom-spa, read the documentation at https://docs.blossomthemes.com/docs/blossom-spa/, and get support at https://blossomthemes.com/support-ticket/.'=>'花团SPA是一款简约典雅的免费WordPress主题，着力服务于美容、水疗行业。有了该主题，不需要任何编程的背景知识，依然能为自己的公司打造功能齐全的专业网站。该主题适合的公司包括：SPA、美容院、理疗中心、按摩店、瑜伽馆、冥想培训班、以及其他传统医疗或医美行业。移动端友好的全面响应式设计让主题根据客户端的屏幕大小而自我调解，保证最佳用户体验。主题简约、利索的设计风格为网站的访问者提供轻松愉悦的浏览体验。不仅如此，主题的代码经过速度优化处理，全面提升网页的加载速度。另外，网页加以Schema.org标记，可帮助谷歌理解你的网站内容，提升搜索排名。通过主题的内置个性化工具， 你可以实时预览网站个性化设置对网站的影响。主题全面结合社交媒体的功能，帮你吸粉并与网站用户保持有效的互动。该主题首页拥有多个功能板块，包括：横幅板块、客服板块、关于我们板块、客服第二板块、行为召唤板块、团队介绍板块、用户推荐板块、以及博客板块。通过这些功能可以用一种得当的方式对公司进行详尽的介绍。该主题提供详尽的使用说明文件，可助你零基础打造自己的博客。不仅如此，迅速亲和的客服团队可随时帮你解决与主题有关的任何问题。查看主题详情：https://blossomthemes.com/downloads/blossom-spa-free-wordpress-theme/
